channel.title: New project OLDSCHOOL
channel.description:
I just downloaded an oldschool source it looks just like 2005 in the good old days. I do not plan on making a remake, but instead adding new content, but keeping the feel of 2005. I need a dev team, and staff, and a CO OWNER so if you are interested download links are below.
The download comes with the client and cache so make sure to put the Cache in your C: then you are good to go! I look forward to meeting some cool people! :) The download should also only take a minute or two since it has no custom models, etc
[img]http://i.imgur.com/eNFRKTi.png[/img]
https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/53833546/Client%20%2B%20cache.rar
